{"tid":2231852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(估國家) 「富二代」闖民宅性侵母女！綁屋主逼看活春宮　逞獸慾一整天","createTime":"2020-10-06T03:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T04:45:51.000Z","uid":229275,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9c7e09a00b2443747140b3c008df5fd6ec8dad66","tid":2231852,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:27:32.000Z","msg":"新北市又一分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">新北市</span>男子李允然去年7月迷姦模特兒姊妹，2被害人憤而提告，李男交保後隨即落跑而被通緝，警方今年2月前往圍捕時又再度逃逸，一不做二不休的他竟持槍侵犯鄰居母女，並將男主人捆起來逼看妻女受辱，在鄰居家待了一整天才離開，其獸行可說天理不容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201006/1825119.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20201006%2F1825119.htm&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=ef9af425\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201006/1825119.htm</a>"},{"pid":"488065420ef8eab94f72c5aced51bed609feb4a5","tid":2231852,"uid":14690,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:30:03.000Z","msg":"癲過av情節"},{"pid":"22c3f1cf2238b697a98566ffba8fc921cf1d8712","tid":2231852,"uid":255637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴撚線"},{"pid":"6854b5fe17c341192e65d143ec31f1ae4710f3e1","tid":2231852,"uid":50041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"台灣好易有槍?前排館長又俾人射,呢單又有槍"},{"pid":"3bb752f144bdb8e3d03bfe261b6ba83b20183a0c","tid":2231852,"uid":131169,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"李允然自知難逃法網，乾脆「一不做二不休」，抱著「多爽一次是一次」的心情敲響隔壁鄰居的門，以送禮為幌子拜訪鄰居母女，進屋後隨即變臉掏槍威嚇2人噤聲。<br />\n<br />\n台灣啲新聞咁多主動形容詞，好似寫故仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7278c8328f2ca5795943ef10d88291330a9a9